United Russia Faces ‘Serious’ Challenge From Left, Shuvalov Says

-- B y   L y u b o v   P r o n i n a
-- 
2011-09-25T08:30:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/united-russia-faces-serious-challenge-from-left-shuvalov-says.html
The United Russia party faces a
“serious” fight with leftist parties in the run-up to
elections, First Deputy Prime Minister  Igor Shuvalov  said today
at a forum held by the ruling party in Moscow.  “We must win in these elections, win by a big margin,”
Shuvalov said. “The fight will be serious, as the leftist mood
in the country has truly become more popular.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lyubov Pronina in Moscow at 
 lpronina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
